text: Cicysium or Kikysion () was the largest of the eight towns of Pisatis in ancient Elis. It is located near the Elean towns of Buprasium and Dymaea, and near Pheraea in Arcadia. Its site is unlocated. ==References== Category:Populated places in ancient Elis Category:Former populated places in Greece Category:Lost ancient cities and towns
title: Cicysium
